				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${R}_{o}=\frac{{S}_{o}}{{S}_{rgi}}$$\end{document}Ro=SoSrgiwhere S
o and S
rgi are overlapping area between RGI2.0 and GGI and the glacier area of RGI2.0, respectively. The overlapping ratio indicates a probability that an ICESat footprint coincides with a glacier area in GGI (Fig. S2).
